high_descs: Go forward to the table then turn left and walk straight until you reach the white shelves in front of you. Face the shelf on your right.
Pick up the gold vase that is on the shelf
Turn in a circle and face the white safe on the floor next to the shelf.
Open the safe, place the vase inside the safe, and shut the safe
anns.task_desc: Put the gold vase into the white safe

high_descs: Take a left at the black table ahead and walk to the white book case to the right of the couch.
Pick up the gold bottle on the shelf above the black statue on the book case.
Turn around, take a left at the couch and turn left to face the white safe next to the fireplace.
Put the gold bottle inside the safe and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a gold bottle in a safe.

high_descs: Move forward, turn left at the end table, walk forward and turn right to face the white shelf.
Grab the golden object from the shelf.
Turn to the right to face the safe.
Place the golden object into the safe.
anns.task_desc: Put the golden object from the shelf into the safe.
